---
import ClientReportLayout from '../../../layouts/ClientReportLayout.astro';
---

<ClientReportLayout title="Action Plan & Roadmap" clientName="1st Home Maintenance">
<nav class="top-nav">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/clients/zolley/" class="nav-brand">Brothers Automate</a>
    <a href="/clients/zolley/">&larr; Back to Overview</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-badge">Action Plan & Roadmap</div>
    <h1>From Invisible to Page 1 in 90 Days</h1>
    <p>A prioritized, step-by-step plan to fix the gaps we found and start getting more calls from customers who are already searching for your services.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIER 1 -->
<section class="tier-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header-bar">
      <div class="tier-number t1">1</div>
      <div class="tier-info">
        <h2>Quick Wins (Week 1-2)</h2>
        <div class="timeline">Low effort, high impact. Do these first.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-cards">
      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Claim Your Google Business Profile</h3>
          <p>You don't appear on Google Maps at all. 40%+ of clicks for "handyman boca raton" go to the map pack. You're missing every single one of those potential customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Create and fully optimize a GBP listing with service categories, business hours, service area, photos, and description</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Appear in Google Maps within 1-2 weeks. Start receiving calls directly from Maps listing.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Fix Missing Meta Descriptions & Duplicate H1</h3>
          <p>Your About and Contact pages have no meta descriptions. Your Contact page has a duplicate H1. These affect how your site appears in search results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Write compelling meta descriptions in Yoast SEO. Fix duplicate H1 tag. Takes 15-20 minutes total.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">20-30% improvement in click-through rates from search results.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Add Testimonials to Your Website</h3>
          <p>Zero testimonials or portfolio on your site. No social proof means visitors have no reason to trust you over competitors with hundreds of reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Reach out to past customers. Add 5-10 testimonials with names and project types. Add before/after project photos.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Increased conversion rate from website visitors to phone calls.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Set Up Professional Domain Email</h3>
          <p>Using 1sthomemaint@gmail.com signals "small and unprofessional" to potential customers. It also hurts email deliverability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Set up Google Workspace or Zoho Mail for info@handymanbocaratonfl.com. Update all contact forms and listings.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Professional credibility + better email deliverability. ~$6/month.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIER 2 -->
<section class="tier-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header-bar">
      <div class="tier-number t2">2</div>
      <div class="tier-info">
        <h2>Growth Plays (Month 1-3)</h2>
        <div class="timeline">Build the content machine and start generating reviews.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-cards">
      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Build 5+ Service Landing Pages</h3>
          <p>You have 6 total pages. Each service you offer needs its own dedicated, keyword-optimized page. Right now you're trying to rank one generic page for dozens of different services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Pages to Create</div>
            <div class="value">Plumbing Repairs, Electrical Services, Bathroom Remodeling, Kitchen Repairs, Ceiling Fan Installation, Exterior Repairs, Painting Services</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">5-10x increase in keyword coverage. Each page ranks for its own cluster of service keywords. All have KD 0.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Launch a Review Generation Campaign</h3>
          <p>You have 0 reviews anywhere. Your competitors have 49-286 Google reviews. Without reviews, you won't rank in the map pack and customers won't trust you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Set up automated review request system. Text/email customers after every job with a direct Google review link. Respond to every review.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">15-25 Google reviews in 90 days (assuming 3-5 jobs/week). Enough to enter the competitive map pack.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Start Google Ads for Core Keywords</h3>
          <p>While your organic rankings build, you're missing 480+ monthly searches with high buyer intent. Google Ads can capture this traffic immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Recommended Budget</div>
            <div class="value">$500-1,000/month targeting "handyman boca raton" variations. CPC is ~$9.39, so budget gets you 50-100 clicks/month.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Immediate visibility for high-intent searches. At 10% conversion rate, that's 5-10 new leads/month from ads alone.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="problem-tag">Problem</div>
          <h3>Create Facebook & Yelp Business Pages</h3>
          <p>Zero social media presence. Competitors are active on Facebook, Yelp, BBB, and more. These are free platforms that generate reviews, traffic, and trust signals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Solution</div>
            <div class="value">Create optimized Facebook Business Page and Yelp listing. Add business info, photos, services. Cross-post project photos weekly.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Additional review platforms, local search citations, referral traffic, and the ability to run local Facebook ads.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIER 3 -->
<section class="tier-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header-bar">
      <div class="tier-number t3">3</div>
      <div class="tier-info">
        <h2>Long-Term Dominance (Month 3-6+)</h2>
        <div class="timeline">Build authority and own your market.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-cards">
      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="solution-tag">Growth</div>
          <h3>Content Marketing & Blog</h3>
          <p>Start a blog with how-to guides, seasonal maintenance tips, and project showcases. This builds topical authority, captures long-tail keywords, and gives Google a reason to crawl your site regularly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Content Ideas</div>
            <div class="value">"How to Fix Drywall Damage," "When to Call a Handyman vs. DIY," "Hurricane Prep Checklist for Boca Raton Homeowners," "5 Signs Your Ceiling Fan Needs Replacing"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">2-4 posts/month builds authority within 6 months. Captures informational searches that lead to service calls.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="solution-tag">Growth</div>
          <h3>Location Pages for Surrounding Cities</h3>
          <p>Create dedicated pages for Delray Beach, Boynton Beach, Deerfield Beach, Pompano Beach, and other service areas. Each page targets "[service] [city]" keywords.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Strategy</div>
            <div class="value">5-8 location pages, each with unique content about serving that area, local references, and service-specific details.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Capture search traffic from every city you serve. Most location keywords also have zero difficulty.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card">
        <div class="action-left">
          <div class="solution-tag">Growth</div>
          <h3>Social Media & Community Presence</h3>
          <p>Regular posting on Facebook and Instagram with project photos, tips, and before/after shots. Join local community groups. Build local brand recognition.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="action-right">
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Strategy</div>
            <div class="value">3-4 posts/week on Facebook + Instagram. Before/after photos, quick tips, seasonal content. Engage in local Boca Raton community groups.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome-box">
            <div class="label">Expected Outcome</div>
            <div class="value green">Brand awareness, referral traffic, social proof. Competitors like Bro's Handyman get significant leads from social.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Summary -->
<section class="summary-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <div class="section-label">The Big Picture</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">What 90 Days Could Look Like</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-grid">
      <div class="summary-card">
        <div class="big">6 &rarr; 20+</div>
        <div class="desc">Website pages (each one targets new keywords)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-card">
        <div class="big">0 &rarr; 25+</div>
        <div class="desc">Google reviews (enough to compete in map pack)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-card">
        <div class="big">Page 2 &rarr; Page 1</div>
        <div class="desc">For "handyman boca raton" (KD 0 = very achievable)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Let's Build This Plan Together</h2>
    <p>We'll walk you through each phase, help you prioritize based on your budget, and handle the execution so you can focus on running your business.</p>
    <a href="https://cal.com/james-pinder-simpleflo/free-quiz-audit-automation-brothers" class="btn-cta">
      Book a Free Strategy Call
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">Prepared by Brothers Automate &middot; April 2026</div>
</footer>
</ClientReportLayout>

<style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background: #fdfcfa; color: #1a365d; line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

    .top-nav { padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e6e1; background: #ffffff; }
    .top-nav .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .top-nav a { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .top-nav a:hover { color: #1a365d; }
    .nav-brand { font-weight: 700; color: #1a365d !important; }

    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14532d 0%, #16a34a 50%, #166534 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 9999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #ed8936; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .section-subtitle { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    /* Tier sections */
    .tier-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .tier-section:nth-child(even) { background: #f8f7f4; }
    .tier-header-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .tier-number {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: white; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .tier-number.t1 { background: #16a34a; }
    .tier-number.t2 { background: #3182ce; }
    .tier-number.t3 { background: #7c3aed; }
    .tier-info h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; }
    .tier-info .timeline {
      font-size: 0.875rem; color: #64748b; font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Action cards */
    .action-cards {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .action-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e1;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .action-card.full-width {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .action-left h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .action-left h3 .emoji { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    .problem-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
      border-radius: 9999px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .solution-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f0fdf4; color: #16a34a;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
      border-radius: 9999px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .action-left p { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .action-right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .outcome-box {
      background: #f8f7f4;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    }
    .outcome-box .label {
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .outcome-box .value { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .outcome-box .value.green { color: #16a34a; }

    /* Summary */
    .summary-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffbeb 0%, #fef3c7 100%);
    }
    .summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .summary-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #fde68a;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .summary-card .big {
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a365d; line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .summary-card .desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .cta-section { background: #1a365d; padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; color: white; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: #ed8936; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; transition: all 200ms ease;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { background: #dd6b20; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .footer { padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e8e6e1; }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .action-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    var elements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');
    if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (entry) {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('visible');
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.15 });
      elements.forEach(function (el) { observer.observe(el); });
    } else {
      elements.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('visible'); });
    }
  });
</script>
